HEADWORD: misdating
<hw>misdating</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The assignment of a date to
something at a time when it could not have existed or
occurred.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> anachronism, mistiming.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

